File: internal/server/pki/ca.go
Package: pki
Purpose: Orchestrates file-driven dynamic root key provisioning to split mTLS from server transport authority scopes.
Functions:
func LoadServerCA(cfg config.Config) (*x509.Certificate, *ecdsa.PrivateKey, error). Purpose: Service engine. Binds local system shared transport trust anchors to disk paths.
func LoadDeviceCA(cfg config.Config) (*x509.Certificate, *ecdsa.PrivateKey, error). Purpose: Identity engine. Extracts operational trust material directly from variable filesystem targets.
func loadPrivateKeyFromFile(path string) (*ecdsa.PrivateKey, error). Internal reader. Decodes PKCS8/PKCS1 elliptic curves.
Security Constraints: Separates device clientAuth issuance keys from transport profiles to prevent horizontal privilege escalations.

File: internal/server/pki/ca_test.go
Package: pki_test
Purpose: Runs verification assertions over key ingestion pipelines using temporary OS storage handles.
Functions:
TestLoadServerCA_MissingConfig: Validates safety fallback loops on structural blinks.
TestLoadDeviceCA_FullWorkflow: Simulates full cryptographic boot sequences over ephemeral filesystem storage nodes.

File: internal/server/pki/server_cert.go
Package: pki
Purpose: Fabricates contextual transport certificates on demand.
Functions:
func GenerateDynamicServerCertificate(caCert *x509.Certificate, caPrivateKey *ecdsa.PrivateKey, host string) (*tls.Certificate, error). Dynamic builder. Computes unique serial markers, registers serverAuth extensions, appends host SAN masks.
Security Constraints: Hard-locks issued leaf parameters to prevent utilization inside client authorization handlers.

File: internal/server/pki/server_cert_test.go
Package: pki_test
Purpose: Verifies x509 field constraints match target specification requirements.
Functions:
TestGenerateDynamicServerCertificate_Success: Asserts CommonName generation, chain length limits, and ExtKeyUsage arrays evaluate cleanly.
TestGenerateDynamicServerCertificate_ValidationErrors: Assures empty parameters bounce out gracefully.
